<a href="/questions/746287-the-door-sounds-like-it-is-very-well">The Door sounds like it is very well written and a powerful story but did you find that you liked any of the characters? It may seem shallow but I find I enjoy a book more when there is at least one character that I like. This does not mean that I need to like everything they do.</a>
